  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-16)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2+x-12)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-16)^2+(x^2+x-12)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-16=0 (1) \\\\x^2+x-12=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-16=0\\)\n\\((x-4)(x+4)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2+x-12=0\\)\n\\(D=1+48=49\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{-1-7}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-4\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{-1+7}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=3\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-4)(x+4)=0 \\\\x=-4; x=3\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=4; x=-4 \\\\x=3; x=-4\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-4\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-4\\)",
